Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: z3c.tabular
Version: 0.6.2
Summary: Table with form support based on z3c.form and z3c.table for Zope3
Home-page: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/z3c.tabular
Author: Roger Ineichen and the Zope Community
Author-email: zope-dev@zope.org
License: ZPL 2.1
Description: This package provides a table implementation including form support for Zope3 
        based on z3c.form and z3c.table.
        
        
        .. contents::
        
        ========
         Issues
        ========
        
        - There is still an issue in README.txt sample, the samples are using nested
          ``<form>`` tags. Fix the sample and use real subform templates.
        
        
